  "body": "<!--\r\n   PR title (set in the GitHub PR creation form):\r\n     jas0xf_adversarial_neural_representation (0.27)\r\n\r\n   Target: commaai/comma_video_compression_challenge  master\r\n   Head:   jas0xf/comma_video_compression_challenge:submission/jas0xf_adversarial_neural_representation\r\n\r\n   How to use this file:\r\n     - URLs marked _URL_HERE will be replaced by the real\r\n       https://github.com/jas0xf/... URLs once we push to the fork.\r\n     - The two GIF tags also work as drag-drop placeholders if you'd rather\r\n       have GitHub host them on user-attachments instead of from the fork.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n# submission name:\r\njas0xf_adversarial_neural_representation\r\n\r\n# upload zipped `archive.zip`\r\nhttps://github.com/jas0xf/comma-anr-supplementary/raw/master/archive.zip\r\n\r\n# report.txt\r\n```\r\n=== Evaluation config ===\r\n  batch_size: 16\r\n  device: cuda\r\n  num_threads: 2\r\n  prefetch_queue_depth: 4\r\n  report: submissions/jas0xf_v62_hpac_exp3/report.txt\r\n  seed: 1234\r\n  submission_dir: submissions/jas0xf_v62_hpac_exp3\r\n  uncompressed_dir: /home/runner/work/comma_video_compression_challenge/comma_video_compression_challenge/videos\r\n  video_names_file: /home/runner/work/comma_video_compression_challenge/comma_video_compression_challenge/public_test_video_names.txt\r\n=== Evaluation results over 600 samples ===\r\n  Average PoseNet Distortion: 0.00045701\r\n  Average SegNet Distortion: 0.00067815\r\n  Submission file size: 207,579 bytes\r\n  Original uncompressed size: 37,545,489 bytes\r\n  Compression Rate: 0.00552873\r\n  Final score: 100*segnet_dist + √(10*posenet_dist) + 25*rate = 0.27\r\n```\r\n\r\n# does your submission require gpu for evaluation (inflation)?\r\nyes\r\n\r\n# did you include the compression script? and want it to be merged?\r\nyes\r\n\r\n# additional comments\r\n\r\n![demo full](https://github.com/jas0xf/comma-anr-supplementary/raw/master/assets/demo_full.gif)\r\n\r\n![demo slow](https://github.com/jas0xf/comma-anr-supplementary/raw/master/assets/demo_slow.gif)\r\n\r\nPlease enjoy my whole month of dedication. The writeup is 24 pages — full recipe, ablations, and the adversarial → neural-representation pivot story: [adversarial neural representation writeup](https://github.com/jas0xf/comma-anr-supplementary/blob/master/writeup.pdf).\r\n\r\nNote: this is a non-Quantizr-style method.\r\n\r\nThis submission requires `constriction` and `pyppmd` (added to `pyproject.toml`).\r\n",
